FLOAT PROPERTY IS USED TO WRAP A TEXT AROUND A PARTICULAR IMAGE
1.FLOAT->wraps the text
2.CLEAR->frees the text

sample code

<style>
    div {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 40%;
      
    }

    p {
      font-size: 2em;
      
    }
    img{
      float: left;
    }

    .cat {
      background-color: aquamarine;
      float: left;
    }

    .dog {
      background-color: coral;
      float:right;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      background-color: blueviolet;
      clear: both;
    }
  </style>
